name: WarBird by Sympo Games
description:
Navigate your war plane through the crowded sky, while collecting a number of stars on your way. You are rewarded with how far you fly in the game and you can use these rewards to purchase other warbirds/planes.
Try and avoid crushing land and keep an eye out for the homing rockets

How to play

Move the plane up by tapping your screen, this gives it some propulsion before gravity begins to send the plane down

Features

Addicting game play.
8 bit graphic.
